column2: SELECT TOP # s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_eqw, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_eqw, g.h_alpha_flux, g. h_alpha_eqw, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_eqw, w.w1mpro as w1, w.w2mpro as w2, w.w3mpro as w3, w.w1snr, w.w2snr, w.w3snr FROM  WISE_xmatch AS x JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON x.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON x.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid JOIN GalSpecLine AS g ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE  (s.class = &&& or s.class = &&&) AND s.z < # AND g.sigma_balmer < #/# AND s.snmedian_g > # AND s.snmedian_r > # AND g.oiii_#_flux > # AND g.h_beta_flux > # AND g.h_alpha_flux > # AND g.nii_#_flux > # AND p.nChild = # AND g.oiii_#_flux > #*g.oiii_#_flux_err AND g.h_beta_flux > #*g.h_beta_flux_err AND g.h_alpha_flux > #*g.h_alpha_flux_err AND g.nii_#_flux > #*g.nii_#_flux_err
